## Bindings: tBinding.sys

## KEY
# Close window (alt-x)
# Maximize (alt-m)
# Full-screen Maximize (alt-f)
# Minimize (thumbnail) (alt-t)

## MOUSE
# Move window (Super+left mouse click)
# Resize window (Super+right mouse click)
# FvwmExpose (Mouse middle-click anywhere on desk)

## Key commands
# A = Alt
# C = Control
# S = Shift
# M = Meta (Alt)
# Super = WinIcon

## KEY-MOUSE BINDINGS (untag below lines)

